Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.74,0:00:02.73,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这里就是学校的菜园
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.73,0:00:04.55,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,抚子很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.55,0:00:06.96,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,花也是 蔬菜也是 她什么都能种
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.96,0:00:08.32,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这就是所谓的「绿拇指」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:10.22,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,萨姆？谁？是男人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.22,0:00:13.10,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不是 说的是植物种得很好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:13.84,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,萨姆吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:14.99,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不是！是大拇指啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:15.60,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:18.27,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶你真是只会说不知所谓的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.27,0:00:19.95,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 那里有什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:21.90,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 那个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.90,0:00:24.42,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,抚子 这朵花叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:27.37,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 这是香桃木
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.37,0:00:29.61,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,既能入药 又能酿酒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.61,0:00:31.61,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,还有 果实似乎也能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.61,0:00:32.47,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:32.79,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}我要吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:35.79,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,感觉 有点像星星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:38.97,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,有鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:41.44,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊晶不行不行 这不好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.44,0:00:42.07,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.07,0:00:44.33,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,如果和水里的倒影对上眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:45.95,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,三天内就会死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.95,0:00:46.60,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.60,0:00:48.18,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,刚刚对上眼了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.18,0:00:50.63,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,对上了…吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.63,0:00:53.34,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,死…要死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.34,0:00:54.58,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我要死了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:00:57.31,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实 别说得太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.31,0:01:00.41,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我觉得这只是为了避免失足落水的说法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.38,0:01:03.58,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,小心点啊 叶香
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.85,0:01:06.91,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以说小心点 要掉下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.63,0:01:10.21,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,比起对上眼睛 看向河水更不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:14.67,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.43,0:01:18.24,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要获得吾野柔术的免许皆传！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.24,0:01:19.90,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,然后和食蚁兽搏斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.90,0:01:21.44,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要变得非常聪明！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.69,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吃得下很多蘑菇！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.69,0:01:26.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,绝对要找到小人！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.30,0:01:27.85,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,真厉害啊 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.85,0:01:28.88,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:30.77,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哈哈 被夸了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:32.81,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,喂 静留你为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.88,0:01:34.25,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什么为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.25,0:01:36.07,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,为什么要这么厉害呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:37.25,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为什么厉害？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:37.86,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:40.25,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是呢 为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.25,0:01:42.20,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,因为想做所以要做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:44.09,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,因为想去所以要去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.09,0:01:45.15,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,大概是这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.15,0:01:46.58,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.95,0:01:48.95,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我什么都…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:50.22,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那就为我应援吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:50.83,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.83,0:01:52.57,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,哦 我会应援的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:54.54,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,只是应援的话 我也是做得到的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:55.66,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我也是！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:56.92,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我也会应援的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:01:58.67,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为叶香的事情应援
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.67,0:02:00.04,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,超努力地应援！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:00.67,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.67,0:02:01.33,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.71,0:02:07.28,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,向那闪耀的约定之星起誓吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:08.66,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,约定之星？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:10.36,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我刚刚给它取的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:12.91,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,它的名字不是「天狼星」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:16.04,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那就把那个作为我们独有的称呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.04,0:02:16.86,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,可以哦
