Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:25.35,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,叶香现在还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:26.90,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,肯定很有精神啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:27.91,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,她看到我们会惊喜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:28.47,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:31.24,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,肯定会很高兴的 见到大家的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:33.29,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,如果去池袋花的时间太久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:36.29,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们变成老太太就不好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:37.18,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,变不成的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:38.70,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们会先变成动物的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:40.21,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,动物吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:42.97,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,松田小姐他们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:46.56,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是说长了蘑菇之后寿命就会变短吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:49.22,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,快的人一年就会死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.73,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,她确实这么说过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:53.85,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,但是活着的时候会很幸福吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:54.93,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:57.43,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶你怎么想？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:04:58.43,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,什么怎么想？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:04:59.77,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,比如说啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:02.01,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,如果你能看一本很有趣的书的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:04.39,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那比其他人死得早一点 你愿意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:06.56,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,能不能别说这种话题了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:08.58,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,但是那些人马上就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:09.47,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:12.08,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,晶很害怕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:15.95,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,即使这么害怕 她还是救了我们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:17.66,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:18.55,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:19.62,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,对不起 晶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:20.33,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:24.44,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,说起来 刚刚你和波奇一直在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:27.32,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,波奇一直在闻你屁股嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:28.44,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你没换内裤吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:28.80,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,哈？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.36,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实你等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.24,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:33.91,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,您更换您的裤衩…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:34.77,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,才不是这个意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.56,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,刚刚不是才洗了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:38.16,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你也看到我换了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:39.84,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:41.36,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶你是藏起来换衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:43.72,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,但那之后不是一起晒衣服的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:44.65,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 确实晒着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:45.58,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,笨蛋玲实
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.20,0:05:51.28,Signs_WText,Sign,0,0,0,,{an7\fs90\fad(600,0)\bord0.6\pos(1187.998,818.668)}第4话    为什么你要把屁股藏起来？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:54.04,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,武藏横手站到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:01.68,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:03.96,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,看上去没危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:06.06,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,什么都没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:08.78,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,总之也不是很潮湿 不也挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:11.04,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,快看快看 山羊山羊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:14.59,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说起来 武藏横手站附近\N因为山羊而很有名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:15.52,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,是因为那只山羊吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:16.66,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,应该不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:17.70,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,它站起来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:19.84,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,武藏横手站的羊是两脚站立的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:20.98,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:22.61,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,才不是！根本没听说过啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.62,0:06:24.59,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:26.24,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯？它是不是往这来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:27.78,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,来了来了来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:41.11,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊那个？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:42.28,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,和巴风特一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:43.43,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那些原来是头盔吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:44.24,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那能对话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:46.29,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,喂 别冲过来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:50.35,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是不是不是那些头盔怎么回事？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:55.64,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,巴风特的历史可以追溯到 14 世纪\N当时国王腓力四世盯上了圣殿骑士团——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:56.24,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,波奇！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.35,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不怕不怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.60,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,静留！快点快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:06:59.94,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,{\an8}在加速了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:16.10,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那些山羊怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:18.10,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,他们想干什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:19.44,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:24.07,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那种东西 不会接下来28站都这样吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:25.90,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,停下吧 别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:34.44,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,轮班驾驶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:35.09,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:37.18,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不能全靠静留你一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:37.97,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,的确啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:41.95,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留确实从吾野开始就一直在开车呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:43.37,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:45.82,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是我自己说要去池袋的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:47.75,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这和现在的话题没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:48.98,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,也不是没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:49.96,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.19,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,是啊 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:52.50,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶你怎么想？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.21,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:55.73,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你也觉得大家轮班驾驶比较好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:57.70,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,啊 说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:07:58.70,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,对吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:07:59.81,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,毕竟嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:02.65,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,为啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:03.19,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:04.50,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你为什么这么想？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:08.89,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,那是…单纯因为疲劳驾驶很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:12.83,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,轮班驾驶的话 电车行驶的时间也增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:14.04,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,效率更高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:16.12,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,也能更快到池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:16.91,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:18.72,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我和晶一个看法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.75,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,对吧 只有好处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:22.68,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:25.17,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留你也要好好休息哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:28.03,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,毕竟不知道还有多久才能到池袋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:29.58,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,玲实你还学到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.58,0:08:31.43,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,明明之前才说三天就能到来着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:32.49,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:34.45,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,但是区区玲实能驾驶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:35.49,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,当然能了！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:36.59,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你知道「电车GO!」的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:38.65,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我之前玩过那样的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:40.98,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那吃完饭叠完衣服之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:42.48,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就是静留的驾驶课堂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:43.23,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:44.82,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那就吃快点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:48.65,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我以前还讨厌苦瓜来着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:50.10,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,最近感觉挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:50.79,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我变成大人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:53.96,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,正因为这种情况\N所以感觉特别好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:58.73,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我现在知道猫哥他们为什么\N要花那么多钱买吾野产的苦瓜了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:00.34,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,虽然苦 但是也有甜味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:02.02,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,还有「鲜味」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:03.25,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 我懂我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:04.40,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,鲜味 鲜味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:08.45,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我现在一天不吃苦瓜反而难受了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:09.74,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我超懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:11.62,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:12.45,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:13.86,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,要我陪你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.06,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,没事 我一个人就行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:16.33,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哦 上得开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:19.98,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,如果外表可爱点 那就完美了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:29.08,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,「身上长蘑菇的人 快的一年就死了」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.08,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我不是！没事没事！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:33.39,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,绝对没问题的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:35.88,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这不是蘑菇 只是生疮了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:38.22,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我是很容易生疮的体质
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.85,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,Don't worry. No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:41.59,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,龙彦保佑我平安！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:21.64,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,逃吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:22.57,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,抚子 加速！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.57,0:10:23.52,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:41.87,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶 到这来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:45.07,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不好好洗澡的话 又要被波奇闻屁股了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:46.16,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,闭嘴 笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.32,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,零分玲实！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:17.65,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,平稳 宁静
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:20.99,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,真想永远在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:32.56,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留 停 还是不停？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:34.48,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,总之先不停
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:35.68,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,就这样慢慢向前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:38.93,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留 好多高尔夫球哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.93,0:11:41.12,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,真的耶 好多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:42.12,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不妙！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:42.91,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:44.65,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不妙不妙不妙不妙！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:45.33,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}玲实 你这样有点吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:46.31,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,快说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:47.98,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我有个不妙的猜想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:50.83,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,武藏横手站的山羊人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:52.84,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,高丽站的根一样的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.31,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,还有这里的高尔夫球是不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:58.30,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,全都是原先车站周边的居民…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:05.00,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:12.08,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,人变成了高尔夫球！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:13.01,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}不要啊—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:18.76,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 受够了 讨厌讨厌讨厌讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.76,0:12:20.55,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,为什么都是这么些可怕的车站呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:22.25,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留 快点搞定吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:24.00,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,刚才说的那个 什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:25.07,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,午餐包裹？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:26.56,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是「之字形转弯」
Comment: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:28.97,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs10\c&HA67656&\pos(240,107)\3c&HF8F0E6&}Hanno
Comment: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:28.97,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs10\c&HA67656&\3c&HF8F0E6&\pos(532.5,27.5)}Higashi-Hanno
Comment: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:28.97,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5\fs10\c&H845D4E&\3c&H845D4E&\pos(358.5,169)\frz333.1}Seibu Ikebukuro Line
Comment: 1,0:12:25.30,0:12:28.97,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs10\c&H4B4848&\3c&HF5F7F2&\pos(358.5,169)\frz333.1}Seibu Ikebukuro Line
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:28.97,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,从现在开始要把车尾转成车头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:30.71,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,把车厢里的行李挪一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:31.45,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:33.36,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真就一路上都只有吓人的车站嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:35.22,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,而且还越来越可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:38.81,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真想遇见能沟通的事物 \N就算像吾野一样 不是人类也无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.81,0:12:40.18,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,才不是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:42.60,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你一定是又想嘲笑我了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:45.12,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,能沟通就意味着…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:48.93,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,可能会说谎 也可能会说些不好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:50.94,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,甚至还可能吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.53,0:12:54.89,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,如果能减少一个争执的起因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:57.62,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我觉得 就算为此变得不能说话也不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.62,0:13:00.44,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,就这样静静地待着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:03.35,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,在阴暗、安静而潮湿的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.06,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,诶 什么什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:06.10,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你想干什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:07.56,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,为什么你要把屁股藏起来？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:08.79,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我才没藏！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:10.63,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:12.56,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,让我看一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:13.11,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:13.84,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,让我看看！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:14.91,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:16.93,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,小气！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.93,0:13:18.40,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你以为我会这么说着就放弃了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:18.61,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:19.58,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我才不！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.14,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,让我们好好确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:28.49,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,晶 这不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:29.71,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不是不是不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:30.48,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,从什么时候开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:31.24,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我没事的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.78,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我什么问题都没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:33.74,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,发生什么事情了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:35.29,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,晶长蘑菇了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:35.87,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:37.86,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我这边抓稳了 那边就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:39.56,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不要 别拔出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:41.84,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我好不容易才得到了安宁！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:42.41,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你这笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:44.49,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,就这么放着不管的话过一两年会死的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:45.07,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,那也无所谓吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:46.73,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,悲观主义挺帅的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:51.10,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我才不想在这个莫名其妙的世界里\N担惊受怕地活着！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:53.21,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶从以前开始就一直是这副样子！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:55.72,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,愤世嫉俗又话痨 还动不动就小瞧别人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:56.39,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:58.18,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,零分玲实灵长类！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:00.29,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不管发生什么都不告诉别人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:02.60,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,就算大难临头了也还在逞强！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:05.06,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}蘑菇 蘑菇 蘑菇！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:07.40,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,明明就是个非常胆小的爱哭鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:19.59,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这到底是个啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:21.18,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.13,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:23.17,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,喂！晶！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.28,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,晶 你还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:25.42,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,晶！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:31.03,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,玲实 静留 还有抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:32.75,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,大家好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:35.35,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,晶无论什么时候都很精神哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:36.95,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,精神饱满！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:39.30,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:40.39,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,在——
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:42.39,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,感觉有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:44.91,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,抚子你在说什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:46.52,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,晶才不奇怪呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:47.40,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,哼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:48.48,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:50.62,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}哼 哼 哼哼哼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:50.73,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们那时候不是变回来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:52.07,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,喂 玲实！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:54.10,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,说话这么大声！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:54.61,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,坏蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:58.53,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是不是因为蘑菇生长过度了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:14:59.98,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,毕竟长得真的很大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:00.50,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:03.32,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你是说我们把不该拔的东西也一起拔出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:04.63,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,总之先让她坐起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:05.58,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,起来吧 晶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:07.09,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,好——
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:10.54,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:11.93,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,呜诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:12.97,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:16.19,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,感觉身体好像不听使唤了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:17.39,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:21.28,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这是…我的错？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:24.55,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,很舒服吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:26.58,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}很可爱吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:28.07,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,是灵魂 我把她的灵魂拔出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:29.57,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}很放松吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:30.89,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶那讨厌的文青之魂！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.35,0:15:32.16,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:33.73,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,地图上找不到像是医院的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:37.05,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,果然天鹅仙人的地图 不对 涂鸦 根本没用嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:38.12,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,回吾野吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.74,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,现在可能退潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.74,0:15:41.58,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就算回去了也没人能治好她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.30,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而且铁路都弯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:46.61,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,如果晶就这么死掉了该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:48.35,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这种事情不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:50.25,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,冷静点 会没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.25,0:15:50.93,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:52.90,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,肯定能治好她的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:53.47,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:55.92,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,可是 都怪我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:16:00.92,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,从今天起 你的名字就叫作安东尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:06.35,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,求你了 善治郎先生\N告诉我们接下来该怎么办吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:09.65,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不管以后发生什么\N我都不会再骂你是糟老头了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:10.76,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:13.45,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,看来这是直接作用到了脑部！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:14.30,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,交给我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:15.74,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你们既然在饭能…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:19.56,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「有一个说话不留情的好医生」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:22.57,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「以前是我的同事」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:27.27,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「在小学的时候 把脱粪的事情 推到我头上」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:33.10,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「作弊的事 竖笛 涂满唾液的事 全都推到我头上了」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:36.34,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「现在在稻荷山公园 帽帽帽……」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:42.03,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}这个糟老头！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:42.41,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,稻荷山…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:44.59,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,他说的是稻荷山公园？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:46.11,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 我觉得是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:47.73,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 咖喱味的大便！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:49.58,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,大便的话题已经结束了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:50.35,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:51.72,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶那时候告诉过我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:56.00,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,稻荷山公园有一个好医生 和代先生说过的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:56.49,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:58.09,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,和代先生是指那只水豚？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:16:58.83,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,她是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:01.22,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不过不知道是谁 甚至不知道是不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:05.71,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说到底稻荷山公园现在变成什么样子了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:07.02,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不要慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:07.92,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:13.87,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,踏踏实实 但也要尽快地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:25.92,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:28.61,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留 那边怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:32.19,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 那个 一个人都没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:43.12,station_sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H666060&\3c&HF5F0EB&\fs32\pos(733.6,354.6)}元\N加\N治
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:34.82,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是有厕所可以上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:36.32,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,水也能流通
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:38.01,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那我也去一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:39.22,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:40.21,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.21,0:17:41.24,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:42.37,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我会照顾晶的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.19,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:45.20,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,终于有个能对话的了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:46.30,Default,Jizo,0,0,0,,那是当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:47.44,Default,Jizo,0,0,0,,别小看地藏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:49.20,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,稻荷山公园是个什么样的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:50.78,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那里有人类医生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:52.31,Default,Jizo,0,0,0,,别问我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:54.03,Default,Jizo,0,0,0,,我们在这里动弹不得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:56.79,Default,Jizo,0,0,0,,不过啊 动不了之后反而特别轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:18:00.34,Default,Jizo,0,0,0,,只不过难得有贡品却没法享用 有点恼火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:03.40,Default,Jizo,0,0,0,,稻荷山公园站要从这再往前两站吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:04.77,Default,Jizo,0,0,0,,除此之外我就全都不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:06.00,Default,Jizo,0,0,0,,医生什么的也不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:07.06,Default,Jizo,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Comment: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:08.15,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\bord2.667\c&H303126&\fs40\3c&HA6906D&\move(705.563,29.333,-54.325,29.333,26,1068)}入间市
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:26.78,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,内脏 内脏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:29.41,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,内脏～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:35.09,station_sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs50\frx0\fry16\pos(410,398)}稻\N荷\N山\N公\N园
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.81,0:18:42.18,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,所以就这样 抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:43.36,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:43.84,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:45.72,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留 拜托看好玲实哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:46.70,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:48.56,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,为什么要看好我？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:51.53,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,因为你有时只看得见眼前 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:53.65,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？说谁呢？我？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:55.18,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是很懂你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:03.87,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,切 这里什么都没有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:05.12,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:07.46,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,别说医生了 什么人都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:11.27,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么铃响了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:12.83,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,在那边！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:15.45,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯…好像有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:16.97,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,看着像墙一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:18.80,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 怎么可能…我完全看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:21.17,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不愧是视力25的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:23.42,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不不 只是2.5而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:25.98,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,铃声停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:26.78,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,过去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:29.98,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留！看 是城镇！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:32.37,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,只是看上去没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:34.73,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是刚才传出了奇怪的铃声吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:35.52,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,有的 有的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:37.61,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那肯定是人搞出来的铃声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:40.06,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们先围着转一圈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:41.21,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}不行 我们没那么多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:44.78,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们得快点找到医生 带去晶那里看看情况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:50.37,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好近！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:52.00,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不如说是好小！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.88,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这是什么情况？格列佛游记吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:55.71,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,感觉有点可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:57.62,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,简直就像世界公园一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:20:00.06,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我觉得那个更小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:02.48,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,果然什么人都没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:03.95,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,看上去确实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:08.94,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,飞机？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:11.02,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,好厉害 好久没有见到过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:20.52,Default,Group,0,0,0,,疼疼疼疼疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:20.75,Default,Group,0,0,0,,{\an8}咋了咋了咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:21.50,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,好疼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:23.36,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,比起疼更多是痒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:24.20,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.65,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎么回事 好痒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:28.48,Default,Group,0,0,0,,痒痒痒痒痒痒痒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:29.46,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,呃啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:34.19,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:35.80,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,一群人偶！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:42.03,Default,Group,0,0,0,,痒痒痒痒痒痒痒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:45.18,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:46.58,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,到底有多少啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:48.09,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}听我说啊 我们不是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:55.44,Default,Group,0,0,0,,疼疼疼疼痒痒痒痒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:03.86,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:08.74,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:11.25,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶 等等我！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:16.00,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,呼 终于追上你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:16.76,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Comment: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:20.75,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\bord2.667\fs10.667\fax0.2\pos(347.813,251.333)\frz336.5\3c&H705D65&}Iron Monty's\N{\fscx70}Splendid Wednesday
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.76,0:21:20.75,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,明天的国语考试\N我完全不知道该怎么学！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:22.82,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,教教我怎么得分！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:25.75,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我要是告诉你了\N你不就不是零分玲实了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.75,0:21:27.16,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是才好呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.16,0:21:28.77,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我不想当零分玲实啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.57,0:21:33.60,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,教材啊 字典啊 把想记住的部分撕下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:35.44,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,夹在东乡煎饼中间吃下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:37.94,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,哇 厉害！不愧是晶！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:50.36,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,疼疼疼疼疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:21:56.80,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:02.18,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.76,0:22:08.02,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这咋回事啊？？？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:36.28,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Ga-tan go-ton ga-tan go-ton
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:39.67,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Shoo shoo train 終 終 トレイン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:41.52,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Ga-tan go-ton ga-tan go-ton
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:44.42,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,しょっちゅう 停止 停止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.05,0:02:48.88,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,仲良くゆこう 電車乗って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:54.15,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,大好きなもの リュックに詰めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:03:00.88,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,ほらここが始発駅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:08.42,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,ラララ 知らない場所へ導いて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:14.38,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,キミを探す旅へ出るのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.34,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Ga-tan go-ton ga-tan go-ton
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:19.12,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,ワクワクスル
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:21.65,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Ga-tan go-ton ga-tan go-ton
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:25.22,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,響け ホイッスル
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:30.32,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,世界が脱線しちゃっても大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:35.18,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,ワタシたちは進んでく どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:43.75,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,次はどんな扉を開けようか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:49.06,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,さあ 終わんない旅へ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:54.10,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Ga-tan go-ton ga-tan go-ton
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:36.28,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,哐当 咕咚 哐当 咕咚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:39.67,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,咻 咻 train 终 终 列车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:41.52,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,哐当 咕咚 哐当 咕咚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:44.42,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,总是 停止 停止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.05,0:02:48.88,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,我们亲密地乘上电车出发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:54.15,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,将喜爱的东西装进背包
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:03:00.88,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,来吧 这里就是 始发站
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:08.42,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,啦啦啦 列车带着我们驶向未知的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:14.38,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,开启寻找你的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.34,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,哐当 咕咚 哐当 咕咚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:19.12,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,心动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:21.65,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,哐当 咕咚 哐当 咕咚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:25.22,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,鸣响吧 汽笛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:30.32,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,即使世界脱轨也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:35.18,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,我们会继续向前 不管去往何方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:43.75,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,列车的门扉再次打开时 那又会是怎样的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:49.06,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,走吧 踏上永不完结的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:54.10,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,哐当 咕咚 哐当 咕咚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.53,0:22:18.17,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,優しい人のなり方を 誰か教えてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.17,0:22:25.65,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,頼れる人のなり方を 誰か教えてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.73,0:22:44.65,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,雨に濡れて傘も差せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.56,0:22:48.38,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,いることもどうでもよくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.37,0:22:52.18,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,明るさが急に怖くなって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.69,0:22:56.45,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,大丈夫じゃないよ 大丈夫じゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.25,0:23:00.68,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,一緒に歩くの嫌になって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:04.65,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,でもひとりでいたいわけじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.04,0:23:08.35,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,目を合わせて笑えなくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.93,0:23:13.70,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,大丈夫じゃない それは大丈夫じゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.05,0:23:18.58,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,何度 傷つけ 間違って 失敗して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.88,0:23:23.05,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,優しさ蔑ろにしただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:26.65,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,傷ついて 許して 許されて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.95,0:23:30.43,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,お前は生きろと言われただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.96,0:23:34.35,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,みんなひとりぼっちだけど 孤独だけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.78,0:23:38.08,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,あなただけここにいれば 孤独じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.53,0:22:18.17,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,多希望有人能告诉我 如何成为一个温柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.17,0:22:25.65,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,多希望有人能告诉我 如何成为一个可靠的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.73,0:22:44.65,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,任由雨水打湿自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.56,0:22:48.38,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,也无所谓撑不撑伞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.37,0:22:52.18,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,突然对光明感到恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.69,0:22:56.45,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,我很不安啊 我很不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.25,0:23:00.68,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,变得讨厌与他人并肩而行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:04.65,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,但又并非是想要孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.04,0:23:08.35,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,我们视线相交 却无法展露笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.93,0:23:13.70,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,我很不安啊 这很不对劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.05,0:23:18.58,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,我无数次伤害你 误会你 犯下错误
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.88,0:23:23.05,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,那都是因为我忽视了你的温柔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:26.65,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,我受到伤害 宽恕他人 被他人谅解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.95,0:23:30.43,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,这都是因为你曾鼓励我活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.96,0:23:34.35,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,虽然大家形单影只 但这绝非孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.78,0:23:38.08,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,只要你仍身处此地 这便不是孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.01,Signs_WText,annotation,0,0,0,,本视频由S1百综字幕组汉化\N仅供学习交流,严禁用于商业用途,请于24小时内删除
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.62,0:00:15.74,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,「萨姆」是 green thumb 的 thumb
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.90,0:01:24.69,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,这里的星空据说取景于\N吾野的东乡公园周边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.43,0:01:19.90,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,免许皆传是最高级别的证明\N拥有该许可之人可以\N自己开宗立派传授技艺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:03.96,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,蘑菇T恤是在东吾野时受赠的\N玲实穿的T恤是\N《练马之国的爱丽丝》中的爱丽丝\N这件T恤是静留的私物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:14.59,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,日铁道杂草除不尽\N羊群出动帮除草
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:55.64,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,巴风特是基督教的羊头恶魔\N也是撒旦的代名词\N1307年10月13日星期五\N法国国王腓力四世镇压了圣殿骑士团\N逮捕了大批法国圣殿骑士并使用酷刑逼供\N巴风特这一名字在几份供述中出现\N被承认为圣殿骑士们崇拜的偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:44.24,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,走遍世界的黑豹车队\N知道如何应对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:43.37,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,可以从电车上获取到\N直流交流皆可的电能\N它的插座在座位下面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:38.65,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,「电车GO!」为电子游戏公司太东\N制作的列车营运与驾驶游戏系列
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:41.59,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,晶把涩泽龙彦称为龙彦 (Tatsuhiko)\N有时也叫涩龙 (Shibutatsu)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:55.00,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,天空充满了光晕\N真实的光晕是在太阳周围形成的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:15.00,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,此处的植物是高丽参\N本站是高丽站
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:34.30,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,7G之后偶尔能在\N河里抓到秋刀鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:45.07,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,在河里洗澡不用沐浴露\N这是礼仪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:52.53,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,7G为数不多的好处之一是夜空更干净\N木星、海王星、龙宫星和月之暗面也清晰可见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:18.76,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,饭能站变成树的人\N看起来似乎都很开心\N实际怎样就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:25.07,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,Lunch Pack
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:26.56,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,Switchback
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:28.49,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,是金针菇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:21.28,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,金针菇移动过的地方\N会留下一条黏糊糊的痕迹\N弄不干净
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:29.41,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,抚子是吾野弓术的大师\N吾野弓术也有打击技
